data.description: This incredible 4-bed, 2-bath manufactured home sits on a nearly 13-acre lot, mostly wooded, providing the perfect backdrop for those who appreciate nature. Step into this turnkey home where your comfort & convenience have already been considered. Furnishings are included, making it a breeze to settle in. The large kitchen features a center island, offering lots of counter space & storage. Discover a 16x40 outbuilding, complete with a shop area & two outdoor stalls. This space is perfect for a variety of hobbies. A small pond adds to the charm of the property, providing a peaceful setting for relaxation. For those looking to embrace a homesteading lifestyle, this property is well-equipped with a chicken coop & run, offering the opportunity to raise your own poultry. Outdoor enthusiasts will love the inclusion of a deer stand already in place, providing the perfect vantage point for hunting or wildlife observation on your own land. This property is a haven for nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts.
